# ---- Generated CAD/print artifacts ----
# Source of truth is the parametric .py + params.json; geometry is reproducible
# output and is regenerated on demand. Only known-good prints are committed
# explicitly (see docs/git-strategy in README). Everything else stays ignored.
projects/**/artifacts/
# Any model built in place (e.g. the packaged examples) also writes ./artifacts/.
**/artifacts/
# API-served build output (StaticFiles mount at /artifacts).
.agent-cad-builds/
scratch/
*.gcode.3mf
result.json
slice_info.config
tmp/
.cad-cache/
